<plot>Bette Midler plays a music teacher in this short film. She realizes that she's won the lottery, but then promptly loses the ticket out the window. The short film then follows her exploits to recover the ticket as it is grabbed by a pigeon, blown down the street and into the subway.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?572615</url></doc>
